  "title": "Senior Sous Chef",
  "description": "<p>- Location(s): CBD area, Esplanade MRT, Downtown MRT</p><p>- Working Days: 6 days/week</p><p>- Working Hours: 11am to 11pm (2 hours break)</p><p></p><p>Responsibilities & Requirements:</p><p>- Assist the team in menu planning, inventory management, and ordering supplies.</p><p>- Ensure consistency in the food preparation and presentation.</p><p>- Maintain a clean and hygienic kitchen environment, adhering to all food safety and sanitation guidelines.</p><p>- Assist in managing stock levels, ensuring adequate supply without overstocking.</p><p>- Ability to stay calm under pressure and solve issues quickly and effectively.</p><p>- Able to work in a fast-paced environment.</p><p></p><p>Benefits:</p><p>Product Trainings | Incentives & Allowance | Annual Leave | Medical Benefits | Dental Benefits | Staff meals</p><p></p><p>We look forward to working with you!</p>",
